node.text: One brew at a time...morning & afternoon filter brews...loving my new coffee beans from @homeground.coffee & @doubleup.coffee for home brewing during CB WFH. Ending April & welcoming month of May with these lovely Mokka processed & natural processed Colombia coffee beans with awesome tasting notes. Thank God tomorrow is Labour Day public holiday!
